        <updateDate>2019-07-26T21:56:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Level the Playing Field in Global Trade Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill requires an expedited trade agreement with a country to meet specified standards regarding wages and production methods for all exported merchandise from that country. </p> <p>]]></text>
      </summary>
